        "english": "Yes, I like it a lot."
      },
      {
        "speaker": "A",
        "gender": "female",
        "spanish": "A mí también me gusta.",
        "english": "I like it too."
      },
      {
        "speaker": "B",
        "gender": "male",
        "spanish": "¿Te gustan los deportes?",
        "english": "Do you like sports?"
      },
      {
        "speaker": "A",
        "gender": "female",
        "spanish": "Sí, me gustan los deportes.",
        "english": "Yes, I like sports."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "title": "Lesson 3:\nCommon Actions",
    "description": "Present tense regular -ar verbs. 'Hablar' (to speak): 'hablo' = I speak, 'hablas' = you speak. 'Estudiar' (to study): 'estudio', 'estudias'.",
    "dialogue": [
      {
        "speaker": "A",
        "gender": "female",
        "spanish": "Yo hablo español.",
        "english": "I speak Spanish."
      },
      {
        "speaker": "B",
        "gender": "male",
        "spanish": "¿Tú hablas inglés?",
        "english": "Do you speak English?"
      },
      {
        "speaker": "A",
        "gender": "female",
        "spanish": "Sí, hablo inglés y español.",
        "english": "Yes, I speak English and Spanish."
      },
      {
        "speaker": "B",
        "gender": "male",
        "spanish": "Yo estudio español.",
        "english": "I study Spanish."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
