        "gender": "female",
        "spanish": "Yo necesito agua.",
        "english": "I need water."
      },
      {
        "speaker": "B",
        "gender": "male",
        "spanish": "¿Necesitas ayuda?",
        "english": "Do you need help?"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "title": "Lesson 5:\nTo want",
    "description": "'Querer' (to want): 'quiero' = I want, 'quieres' = you want. Irregular verb. Very common!",
